General.Name: Qliro AB
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Qliro AB (publ) operates as a fintech company. It provides digital checkout payment solutions to e-merchants and their customers in the Nordic region, as well as offers online pay-after-delivery products, including invoicing, Buy Now Pay Later, and various partial payments. The company also offers personal loans and savings accounts, as well as digital financial services to consumers in Sweden. Its payment solutions include payment methods offered through card, direct payments from bank accounts, or PayPal payments. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Qliro AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Qliro Group AB (publ).
